  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdaptiveImageServlet
    The Composum Assets - Adaptive Image Servlet delivers renditions of image assets for the configured variations.
    AssetNodeServlet
    the servlet to 'render' asset resources (delivers the assets default original)
    CommonsServlet
    The servlet to provide changes of the Asset Managers UI.
    ConfigServlet
    The servlet to provide changes of the Asset configuratioon resources.
    ImageAssetServlet
    the servlet to deliver asset originals or volatile configuration example images {/path/to/image(asset)}.asset[.{variation}[.{rendition}]].ext[{/path/to/asset/config}]
